lead_paragraph: Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton prepared for Russian Grand Prix qualifying with the fastest lap yet of the Sochi circuit in Saturday's final practice.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Faster Than Ever in Final Sochi Practice
